author: RTÉ News
title: Shift in consumer spending during Covid19
description: Irish consumers have been spending more on home fitness products, gaming and streaming services during Covid-19.
content:
Analysis of debit card transactions by Bank of Ireland has revealed that Irish consumers have been spending more on home fitness products, gaming and streaming services during Covid-19.
